searchParameters.q: Humboldt County In-Home Supportive Services website

organic.title: In-Home Supportive Services | Humboldt County, CA - Official Website
organic.snippet: Humboldt County IHSS is committed to helping elders, disabled adults and disabled children in Humboldt County live to their highest personal potential.

organic.title: IHSS Eligibility | Humboldt County, CA - Official Website
organic.snippet: To be IHSS eligible in Humboldt County, CA, you must be 65+, blind, or disabled, a CA resident, live alone, receive Medi-Cal, and have low income. Income share may be available.

organic.title: IHSS Website - Login
organic.snippet: Log in to your IHSS account to view timesheets, payment statuses, submit timesheets, request direct deposit, and claim sick leave. User name and password are case sensitive.

organic.title: In-Home Supportive Services (IHSS) Program
organic.snippet: The In-Home Supportive Services (IHSS) program provides in-home assistance to eligible aged, blind, and disabled individuals as an alternative to out-of-home ...

organic.title: In-Home Supportive Services (IHSS) Program | findhelp.org - FindHelp
organic.snippet: The IHSS Program helps individuals who are over 65 years of age, or disabled, or blind obtain services so that they can remain safely in their own home.
